  "detailed_description": "Thallia, a 15-year old girl from the formerly prosperous family crest of Belsoon, has her world upended when her father sells her off to the Labour Force for a few measly coins. How will Thallia deal with this Betrayal of Blood? Will she stand idly by and serve out her indenture? Surely not.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/e0b9475926e72497244f34d32781e4d8.poster.avif?t=1680276522\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/e0b9475926e72497244f34d32781e4d8.webm?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/e0b9475926e72497244f34d32781e4d8.mp4?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"I will gain my freedom, whatever the cost.\"</h2><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2.5D Atmospheric RPG with charming pixel aesthetic<br></li><li>Grounded medieval-era setting - no magic!<br></li><li>A mix of field-overview and 1st-person dungeon-crawling gameplay modes<br></li><li>ATB battles that encourage strategic thought utilizing different weapon and skill types<br></li><li>No set classes - find the best weapon and armour combinations for any given situation<br></li><li>Day/Night cycles with dynamic lighting and shadows<br></li><li>Set within the ever-expanding canon of Strength & Virtue universe<br></li><li>Custom key binding and controller support</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/90a07c0ad8faeb6170d3543a46e9df2a.poster.avif?t=1680276522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/90a07c0ad8faeb6170d3543a46e9df2a.webm?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/90a07c0ad8faeb6170d3543a46e9df2a.mp4?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Thallia, a 15-year old girl from the formerly prosperous family crest of Belsoon, has her world upended when her father sells her off to the Labour Force for a few measly coins. How will Thallia deal with this Betrayal of Blood? Will she stand idly by and serve out her indenture? Surely not.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/e0b9475926e72497244f34d32781e4d8.poster.avif?t=1680276522\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/e0b9475926e72497244f34d32781e4d8.webm?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/e0b9475926e72497244f34d32781e4d8.mp4?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"I will gain my freedom, whatever the cost.\"</h2><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2.5D Atmospheric RPG with charming pixel aesthetic<br></li><li>Grounded medieval-era setting - no magic!<br></li><li>A mix of field-overview and 1st-person dungeon-crawling gameplay modes<br></li><li>ATB battles that encourage strategic thought utilizing different weapon and skill types<br></li><li>No set classes - find the best weapon and armour combinations for any given situation<br></li><li>Day/Night cycles with dynamic lighting and shadows<br></li><li>Set within the ever-expanding canon of Strength & Virtue universe<br></li><li>Custom key binding and controller support</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/90a07c0ad8faeb6170d3543a46e9df2a.poster.avif?t=1680276522\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/90a07c0ad8faeb6170d3543a46e9df2a.webm?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2355010/extras/90a07c0ad8faeb6170d3543a46e9df2a.mp4?t=1680276522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
